import { TextField, Button, Paper, Typography, Stack } from "@mui/material";
import { Container } from "@mui/system";
import React from "react";
import Header from "../components/header";

export default function Login() {
  const paperStyle = {
    padding: "40px",
    width: "28%",
    height: "40%",
    justifyContent: "center",
    alignItems: "center",
  };

  return (
    <>
      <Header />
      <Stack
        dir="rtl"
        direction="row"
        spacing={5}
        sx={{
          minHeight: "650px",
          height: "100vh",
          mt: "-64px",
          justifyContent: "center",
          alignItems: "center",
          "& .MuiTextField-root": {
            paddingBottom: "10px",
            fontSize: "10px",
          },
          "& .MuiButton-root": { fontSize: "12px", px: 4, py: 1.5 },
        }}
      >
        <Paper sx={paperStyle} elevation={7}>
          <Stack sx={{ justifyContent: "center", alignItems: "center" }}>
            <Typography sx={{ color: "#000", mb: "50px" }} variant="h1">
              ورود به حساب کاربری
            </Typography>
            <form>
              <TextField fullWidth label="نام کاربری" variant="outlined" />
              <TextField fullWidth label="رمز عبور" variant="outlined" />
            </form>
            <Button
              sx={{ mt: 10 }}
              type="submit"
              variant="contained"
              color="primary"
              size="large"
            >
              ورود
            </Button>
          </Stack>
        </Paper>
        <Paper sx={paperStyle} elevation={7}>
          <Typography sx={{ color: "#000", mb: "50px" }} variant="h1">
            ساخت حساب کاربری
          </Typography>
          <form>
            <TextField fullWidth label="نام کاربری" variant="outlined" />
            <TextField fullWidth label="ایمیل" variant="outlined" />
            <TextField fullWidth label="رمز عبور" variant="outlined" />
          </form>
          <Button
            sx={{ mt: 3 }}
            type="submit"
            variant="contained"
            color="secondary"
            size="large"
          >
            عضویت
          </Button>
        </Paper>
      </Stack>
    </>
  );
}
